title: Kronan
description: A grocery store chain with several locations. Carries a large selection of vegan products such as fruits and vegetables, peanut butter, soy yogurts, tofu, quinoa, rice, grains, beans, breads, chips. Oven/microwaveable options (samosas, pakoras, etc) are also available. Most, if not all, labels are in English. If buying cheese, watch for rennet, it is more common to put it in cheeses here.
